Sprint #1 User Stories:
User Story 1: As a student, I want a user interface that is customizable to my dietary needs and preferences, so that I can easily find meals that fit my diet.
User Story 2: As a student, I want a user interface that is personalized where I can see my selected recipes and grocery lists for the week, so that all my meal planning is in one place.
User Story 3: As a student, I want a user interface where I can communicate with UHS staff easily and ask any questions I may have. As an admin, I want a user interface where I can respond to student questions regarding meal plans and dietary needs/preferences.

